Name: Stigfinnare
About the game: Learn to improvise during a fight with an opponent in Stigfinnare. Players on 5 different maps with their tasks and features. You will always get a new experience playing this game because everything is random here. Defense a hill with a hairdryer on KOTH map, create your minefield at Trapdoor map, get into enemy bases and steal resources at Electrize map. Fight in a team or split to get the points needed to change your character. You can play with your friends in private lobbies. In this game you will find: Battle for energy at map 'Electrize' Detecting of enemy positions at map 'Destruction' Making decisions fast to reach the finish line first, or turn and try luck on Maze map Creating strategies with set traps on Trapdoor map Epic battles with a hairdryer and blowing off enemies from platforms on KOTH map Hide&Seek on Camouflage map All this you can do in a network game.
